==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Controverter
<hw>Con"tro*ver`ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
controverts; a controversial writer; a controversialist.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Some <qex>controverters</qex> in divinity are like swaggerers in a
tavern.</q> <rj><qau>B. Jonson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Controvertible</ent>⟦br⟧
